{"tid":465683,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好難接受一個想同佢結婚既伴侶散","createTime":"2017-11-11T18:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T18:03:56.000Z","uid":31887,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a17d059588db759dbec300c33aea8d32f9a19a47","tid":465683,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T18:13:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c9306e6b7dd52e270a57c8072f3a2c4d2e7b77","tid":465683,"uid":31887,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T18:14:05.000Z","msg":"寧願一開始被拒絕<br />\n好難振作重新做人"},{"pid":"8ffce0d5313e9c70a2d19e2e87be361cb4c43858","tid":465683,"uid":3908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T18:15:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6786adc0c5a774ec182a33895b2e877db27b6f8d","tid":465683,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T18:15:09.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro"},{"pid":"55094e27fa81f746d9096f3d0ea2334e87e78902","tid":465683,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T18:15:36.000Z","msg":"愛情底線係愛人多過愛自己<br />\n下次唔好啦"},{"pid":"9872d4d21d1b82e8448bb8d068487610afb15c5a","tid":465683,"uid":145352,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T18:16:03.000Z","msg":"被世界遺棄不可怕"},{"pid":"a8c96b0fab85f77081674685534dd42c3baf7a35","tid":465683,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T18:16:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>寧願一開始被拒絕<br />\n好難振作重新做人</blockquote><br />\n巴打唔洗傷心 大把人同你一樣(我自己)~~<br />\n<br />\n好好努力做好自己 等待新的情侶吧</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b3b35c953be24351ab637abb46b3e1dfe219e95","tid":465683,"uid":139720,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T18:16:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愛情底線係愛人多過愛自己<br />\n下次唔好啦</blockquote><br />\n愛一個人最盡就係愛到冇底線"},{"pid":"6aa3858f743ec68acee1ce76558560b5fe61e8c6","tid":465683,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T18:17:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愛情底線係愛人多過愛自己<br />\n下次唔好啦</blockquote><br />\n意志都無埋<br />\n飲酒 日飲夜飲<br />\n飲到朋友都覺得我煩<br />\n唯有自己飲<br />\n原本有個project埋尾<br />\n但真係無動力搞<br />\n好彩唔係打工<br />\n如果唔係又比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948e4c5c9bc01aba6614e1c6027ee7c04ddbc5e3","tid":465683,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T18:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>愛情底線係愛人多過愛自己<br />\n下次唔好啦</blockquote><br />\n愛一個人最盡就係愛到冇底線</blockquote><br />\n以前已經無膽再認真拍拖<br />\n直到遇到佢<br />\n決定賭多鋪<br />\n同人拍拖唔洗咩勇氣 但有勇氣拍拖無底線就真係好難"},{"pid":"5540142c29d1bd2c968303aba80a532da351d69d","tid":465683,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T18:19:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>被世界遺棄不可怕</blockquote><br />\n播藍天啦<br />\n失戀唱情歌同自殺一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f3cff44173812556473ed37c8fef71b620333f","tid":465683,"uid":58119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T18:19:53.000Z","msg":"巴打加油 我知要企返起身再相信愛情係唔容易（我都努力緊）<br />\n你諗住同佢結婚但人地一啲都唔想呢<br />\n要相信下個路口會有一個命中註定嘅人等緊你 就當佢係教你點樣去愛人嘅一個老師啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152dcb53665c29efac3947e51a5607a664fc658d","tid":465683,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T18:21:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打加油 我知要企返起身再相信愛情係唔容易（我都努力緊）<br />\n你諗住同佢結婚但人地一啲都唔想呢<br />\n要相信下個路口會有一個命中註定嘅人等緊你 就當佢係教你點樣去愛人嘅一個老師啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實佢應該想<br />\n只係有時佢想要野 我買唔到比佢<br />\n結果就吵 吵到人都無埋<br />\n如果我係有錢仔咩事都沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e293b90a51e9fdf9b3211cce4c719be34b5679","tid":465683,"uid":58119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited