<br />\n你諗住同佢結婚但人地一啲都唔想呢<br />\n要相信下個路口會有一個命中註定嘅人等緊你 就當佢係教你點樣去愛人嘅一個老師啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實佢應該想<br />\n只係有時佢想要野 我買唔到比佢<br />\n結果就吵 吵到人都無埋<br />\n如果我係有錢仔咩事都沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最少你都學識要收下火</blockquote><br />\n原本想收<br />\n但創業真係唔想拎幾萬銀出黎<br />\n邊有錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n口講想心未必想<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為我情境都好難受<br />\n到覺得無人體諒就吵起上來<br />\n錢銀 萬惡根源"},{"pid":"0bbc1d4e582026fee3f460a64362d2dac083c421","tid":465683,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T18:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2821fa02c10623455bfe616f5d1a9e8f2008ba","tid":465683,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T19:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5686ad38c5ae2ca0a331757d6f4e1321ed433324","tid":465683,"uid":132896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T19:07:44.000Z","msg":"散左之後到而家單身都差唔多一年<br />\n<br />\n飲酒飲密左<br />\n係好彩做野個面比較彈性，有時好憂鬱想玩夜啲<br />\n自己半夜自己諗野夜左都唔怕<br />\n不過間唔中做野個邊都冇乜動力<br />\n<br />\n好左好多啦<br />\n不過依然都係成日出現佢既影子<br />\n<br />\n最錯，或者最唔應該做既<br />\n就係見家長 一過左呢步就會諗多好多野 計劃好多野<br />\n到失去個時形成既反差 真係好誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b205c3476d402cf4b4cb89f7469ce09c38aa47","tid":465683,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T19:12:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>散左之後到而家單身都差唔多一年<br />\n<br />\n飲酒飲密左<br />\n係好彩做野個面比較彈性，有時好憂鬱想玩夜啲<br />\n自己半夜自己諗野夜左都唔怕<br />\n不過間唔中做野個邊都冇乜動力<br />\n<br />\n好左好多啦<br />\n不過依然都係成日出現佢既影子<br />\n<br />\n最錯，或者最唔應該做既<br />\n就係見家長 一過左呢步就會諗多好多野 計劃好多野<br />\n到失去個時形成既反差 真係好誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 見家長係麻煩事<br />\n同佢太多回憶 去邊都諗起<br />\n太多影子<br />\n唔敢搵下個<br />\n好怕將個女仔當做ex影子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ba484f69bb2ba504f08b10c5fd556cfdf57c19","tid":465683,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T19:14:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>散左之後到而家單身都差唔多一年<br />\n<br />\n飲酒飲密左<br />\n係好彩做野個面比較彈性，有時好憂鬱想玩夜啲<br />\n自己半夜自己諗野夜左都唔怕<br />\n不過間唔中做野個邊都冇乜動力<br />\n<br />\n好左好多啦<br />\n不過依然都係成日出現佢既影子<br />\n<br />\n最錯，或者最唔應該做既<br />\n就係見家長 一過左呢步就會諗多好多野 計劃好多野<br />\n到失去個時形成既反差 真係好誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打 一齊努力<br />\n以前戒左酒 唔開心先飲<br />\n依家變左日日飲<br />\n想改返一星期醉一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee3c24489dd0290b25f6c072d2294c3fea8a513","tid":465683,"uid":3908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T19:15:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87ef5cd7fa554d0cd87e8f4d7e368882bbfb28fa","tid":465683,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T19:19:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>散左之後到而家單身都差唔多一年<br />\n<br />\n飲酒飲密左<br />\n係好彩做野個面比較彈性，有時好憂鬱想玩夜啲<br />\n自己半夜自己諗野夜左都唔怕<br />\n不過間唔中做野個邊都冇乜動力<br />\n<br />\n好左好多啦<br />\n不過依然都係成日出現佢既影子<br />\n<br />\n最錯，或者最唔應該做既<br />\n就係見家長 一過左呢步就會諗多好多野 計劃好多野<br />\n到失去個時形成既反差 真係好誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩啊 我果時4年個女朋友都見晒家長 訂埋婚 但係屌你老母最後為左厹離開我<br />\n<br />\n果下真係唔知點~~ 最後用左4個月放低佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n4個月咁快<br />\n過兩招來<br />\n細路生平認真兩次<br />\n上件都麻煩左幾年"},{"pid":"72ff264a2d3aab77fb202837b0dc10514c727b0e","tid":465683,"uid":3908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T19:22:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"565752d1069c126ec399f62a0664ab3acee127b7","tid":465683,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T19:25:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>散左之後到而家單身都差唔多一年<br />\n<br />\n飲酒飲密左<br />\n係好彩做野個面比較彈性，有時好憂鬱想玩夜啲<br />\n自己半夜自己諗野夜左都唔怕<br />\n不過間唔中做野個邊都冇乜動力<br />\n<br />\n好左好多啦<br />\n不過依然都係成日出現佢既影子<br />\n<br />\n最錯，或者最唔應該做既<br />\n就係見家長 一過左呢步就會諗多好多野 計劃好多野<br />\n到失去個時形成既反差 真係好誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩啊 我果時4年個女朋友都見晒家長 訂埋婚 但係屌你老母最後為左厹離開我<br />\n<br />\n果下真係唔知點~~ 最後用左4個月放低佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n4個月咁快<br />\n過兩招來<br />\n細路生平認真兩次<br />\n上件都麻煩左幾年</blockquote><br />\n我由中學同佢拍到大學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n忘記佢就係 鎖撚晒佢全部野<br />\n<br />\n之後努力搵野分散 就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家嬲撚緊佢 唔再掛佢</blockquote><br />\n個人睇法<br />\n你對佢有感覺就未放底哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我第一個愛過既女人<br />\n我對佢咩感覺都無<br />\n以前有恨個陣都以為放底左<br />\n得復仇心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實昆自己"},{"pid":"edd3bceb211f60d57c213f865fed9db48d76168c","tid":465683,"uid":3908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T20:11:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dea22781c12ed890b5e2d973929ac285c9c9a3cc","tid":465683,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T20:51:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>愛情底線係愛人多過愛自己<br />\n下次唔好啦</blockquote><br />\n愛一個人最盡就係愛到冇底線</blockquote><br />\n最好唔好單靠愛情結婚 男女都係"},{"pid":"9e0c7ac40e56adbbe25b41b0d020ab7c0f4000c2","tid":465683,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T20:59:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>愛情底線係愛人多過愛自己<br />\n下次唔好啦</blockquote><br />\n愛一個人最盡就係愛到冇底線</blockquote><br />\n最好唔好單靠愛情結婚 男女都係</blockquote><br />\n政婚姻咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 普通人仲可以靠咩"},{"pid":"8c87a7126d26ae414d9b0375d06e9a15a71d3bb2","tid":465683,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T00:23:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>愛情底線係愛人多過愛自己<br />\n下次唔好啦</blockquote><br />\n愛一個人最盡就係愛到冇底線</blockquote><br />\n最好唔好單靠愛情結婚 男女都係</blockquote><br />\n政婚姻咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 普通人仲可以靠咩</blockquote><br />\n你可以同一個有好感既人結婚，但唔好愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01777ccb9177b73b3fba183cb98ff067512afae9","tid":465683,"uid":68676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T00:33:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>愛情底線係愛人多過愛自己<br />\n下次唔好啦</blockquote><br />\n愛一個人最盡就係愛到冇底線</blockquote><br />\n最好唔好單靠愛情結婚 男女都係</blockquote><br />\n政婚姻咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 普通人仲可以靠咩</blockquote><br />\n你可以同一個有好感既人結婚，但唔好愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n.....咁咪姐係為結婚而結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n其實如果雙方都抱住上術個底線拍拖 咁樣咪唔會有結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再講我覺得我自己會變成愛佢多過佢愛我原因係我唔係太吸引佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"015ceee125dc498bb358ecbd723af93aeee76db8","tid":465683,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:05:06.000Z","msg":"有得同佢傾返電話就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5205174ccdd2eaaac5c676f924868b020bb8a947","tid":465683,"uid":157588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T09:57:53.000Z","msg":"雙方見埋家長先最煩，以為認定左對方，佢話走就走左去，得返自己同屋企人交待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6035ca6851ff75fc2a8961861c55af3a513a54b","tid":465683,"uid":19921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:05:00.000Z","msg":"有時真係 你一直做緊既野都係想為佢將來<br />\n為同佢結婚 有一個好好家庭<br />\n但係可以話走就走 話唔愛就唔愛<br />\n你可以點 一路行 但根本無方向"},{"pid":"e30f33101380384e5a8cc034fef86e979f45cc99","tid":465683,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:19:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時真係 你一直做緊既野都係想為佢將來<br />\n為同佢結婚 有一個好好家庭<br />\n但係可以話走就走 話唔愛就唔愛<br />\n你可以點 一路行 但根本無方向</blockquote><br />\n睇化左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條女唔生性 我又燥底<br />\nPlan左既野當一場空<br />\n有時真係話走就走<br />\n拍拖既野真係有酒就今朝醉算"},{"pid":"4949d6fad234cafe8a43d36110dc0f3e650103d4","tid":465683,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雙方見埋家長先最煩，以為認定左對方，佢話走就走左去，得返自己同屋企人交待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYes<br />\n未帶過女仔見家長<br />\n父母知散左了<br />\n好彩無問長問短"},{"pid":"61df93ddf5f04eb74fe912d678a4eac0646a3a44","tid":465683,"uid":46300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T12:19:26.000Z","msg":"宜家唯有努力工作 做一個更好既自己<br />\n希望佢會再一次愛上我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9658a10c570d4fe1793b3c95390362cd32232b","tid":465683,"uid":19921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:01:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜家唯有努力工作 做一個更好既自己<br />\n希望佢會再一次愛上我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗 不停做運動 不停增值自己<br />\n好希望佢返黎我身邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e93228718903a28efd95e2af923ef9e8e9288b5","tid":465683,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:06:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>宜家唯有努力工作 做一個更好既自己<br />\n希望佢會再一次愛上我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗 不停做運動 不停增值自己<br />\n好希望佢返黎我身邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fac